Esker Melchior
{{boring}}

'''Esker Melchior''' is the [[Troll#Troll_for_a_Day_.28TFAD.29|Troll for a Day]] pseudonym used by a poster on the [[Yahoo]]! Finance message board for [[SCO]] Group.

Articles posted under this name are satirical in nature. They tend to repeat pro-SCOX comments and sentiments but use ridiculously poor spelling, grammar and punctuation to make the point that the logic behind some pro-SCOX arguments is also ridiculously poor.  Often Esker is confused with [[George W. Bush]] or [[Darl McBride]].  Esker is not the [[Clicktard]].

The articles weave in recent events and comments in way that makes them hard to dismiss as mere noise, robotically generated text, or [[Santorum]] pro-[[gay]] speeches.

Esker Melchior's comments are amusing enough that they often receive a dozen or more "recommendations" from the [[nerd]]s who have nothing better to do than read a finance board of a stock they don't own.

